Source: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Section: golang
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Docker Hardened Images <dhi@docker.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, binutils, gcc, libc6-dev
Conflicts: golang-1.24, golang-1.25, golang-1.26, golang-1.24-dev, golang-1.25-dev, golang-1.26-dev, golang-msft-fips-1.24, golang-msft-fips-1.25, golang-msft-fips-1.26
Description: Microsoft FIPS Go compiler @MAJOR_MINOR_VERSION@
 Microsoft's fork of Go with FIPS 140 system crypto support via
 the systemcrypto experiment. This package provides the Go
 @MAJOR_MINOR_VERSION@.x release line with FIPS compliance.

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@-oci-config
Architecture: all
Depends: @PACKAGE_NAME@ (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: OCI configuration for @PACKAGE_NAME@
 OCI container configuration (environment variables, directory paths,
 and FIPS 140 settings) for the @PACKAGE_NAME@ package.
